{"tid":1541396,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城大舊生推倒校內民主女神像 庭上普通話答辯認刑事毀壞罪","createTime":"2019-09-04T14:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T07:04:24.000Z","uid":68738,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3ce6b93dfd402233e252aa3a04c747aa7050d7","tid":1541396,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"操普通話的城大舊生今年7月撕毀校內民主牆紙張，繼而推倒放在旁邊的民主女神像，神像着地時頭部破碎，高舉火炬的手臂斷開。報稱任職保險經理的涉案舊生被控刑事毀壞罪，今午在西九龍裁判法院認罪。辯方指他願意向學生會賠償，惟裁判官得悉損毀神像由藝術家免費贈予城大學生會後，決定先讓辯方考慮賠償問題，案件押後至本周五判刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告王錫釗（32歲）承認於今年7月23日在城大楊建文學術樓圖書館外，無合法辯解而損毀屬於城大學生會、價值2.5萬港元的民主女神像。<br />\n<br />\n警誡下稱意外將神像推倒<br />\n<br />\n案情指當日傍晚，有學生看見被告撕走民主牆海報，遂上前要求被告停手。被告未有理會，更進而將民主女神像推倒，過程被閉路電視拍下。事後被告被捕，警誡下自稱是意外把神像推倒。<br />\n<br />\n根據案情，警方向城大學生會調查，會長稱女神像價值2.5萬元。控方指學生會打算訂造一個新的女神像，並呈上2.5萬元報價單，要求被告賠償。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官羅德泉閱後，詢問報價單位是不是一間公司。控方向在場旁聽的學生會幹事索取資料，確認損毀神像是5年前由藝術家製造，送給學生會作為禮物。學生會近期再向藝術家索取報價，獲回覆指新造神像需2.5萬元。<br />\n<br />\n被告現居於深圳<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告願意賠償，惟他表達有關取態時，未知涉案民主女神像屬免費製作。羅官則稱2.5萬元並非少數目，將案件押後兩天至周五（6日）再處理，其間批准被告繼續保釋，但不准他離港，明天須到深水埗警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，被告多年前曾就讀城大，案發時已非該校學生，現時居於深圳，今晨來港應訊。旁聽的城大學生會署理會長黃希朗表示，已着手籌備訂造新民主女神像。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190904/60009122?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F60009122%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJKha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=dcdebdbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190904%2F60009122%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=0db06811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190904/60009122?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"a2c83c20e7f00709725f8c12866a64f1bf88078a","tid":1541396,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMdRo1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMdRo1b.jpg&h=eaebc3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pO6GMew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpO6GMew.png&h=87f304e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NhKUmNS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhKUmNS.jpg&h=2a94de72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvRjxUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvRjxUx.jpg&h=3601ea99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a8a13cc3f590374c3281699d4c32933e582172f","tid":1541396,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"fo